Bill no. should be 7 characters long with 6 numerical characters and one #. # will be the starting character in any bill no.
	
If bill no.re entered is not in this format then “Invalid Bill No.” Should be displayed. 

The amount has to be written only to two decimal places.

If it's not in this format then only consider two decimal places.

Date has to range from 27 August 2003 to 29 January 2024. The format for date is DD/ Month /YYYY.  Eg.  27 August 2003.

Any date outside the range is invalid as the bills are being generated within this range. Any date outside this range should give a message “ Invalid bill”
If the format of date is not valid, user should be prompted to re enter the date. With the message “Format of Date is incorrect”























